text: RNAS Hinstock (HMS Godwit) is a former Royal Navy Fleet Air Arm station located in Hinstock, Shropshire. The following units were here at some point: * No. 27 Maintenance Unit RAF * No. 29 Maintenance Unit RAF * No. 37 Maintenance Unit RAF * 702 Naval Air Squadron * 729 Naval Air Squadron * 734 Naval Air Squadron * 758 Naval Air Squadron * 780 Naval Air Squadron * 798 Naval Air Squadron ==See also== * List of Royal Air Force Satellite Landing Grounds ==References== Category:Royal Naval Air Stations Category:Buildings and structures in Shropshire Category:Military installations closed in 1947
title: RNAS Hinstock (HMS Godwit)
